import { Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Paper, Button } from '@mui/material'; const InventoryList = ({ dataList, handleGetInventory, handleDeleteInventory }) => { const handleGet = (id) => { handleGetInventory(id) } const handleDelete = (id) => { handleDeleteInventory(id) } return ( # Inventory Name Category Price Unit Source Available Quantity Payment Status {dataList.map((inventory, index) => ( {index + 1} {inventory.inventoryName} {inventory.category} {inventory.price} {inventory.unit} {inventory.sourceCompany} {inventory.availableQuantity} {inventory.paymentStatus} ))}
); }; export default InventoryList;
